WEBVTT

00:00:00.566 --> 00:00:01.966
Today we're going to check out

00:00:01.966 --> 00:00:05.199
the portable portal
that just got released by Safe-Portals.

00:00:06.532 --> 00:00:09.366
As you may know, due to security reasons,

00:00:09.366 --> 00:00:12.632
portals used to be required
to be fixed on walls.

00:00:13.166 --> 00:00:16.332
So will this portable version
be a game changer?

00:00:16.932 --> 00:00:19.932
We will find that out today.

00:00:20.332 --> 00:00:23.332
So we're going to set it up in this room

00:00:23.332 --> 00:00:26.332
over here.

00:00:27.032 --> 00:00:28.699
And I'm going to put one portal

00:00:28.699 --> 00:00:31.699
each on the walls over there.

00:00:34.899 --> 00:00:35.766
Opening up,

00:00:35.766 --> 00:00:39.332
the first thing we have here
is the user manual.

00:00:40.399 --> 00:00:42.666
Always good to start with that.

00:00:42.666 --> 00:00:46.132
And we've got two charging cables,
one for each portal.

00:00:47.166 --> 00:00:49.732
The battery life on these portals
is not bad,

00:00:49.732 --> 00:00:52.732
lasting up to 24 hours on a single charge.

00:00:53.932 --> 00:00:56.466
Now we have the portals themselves.

00:00:56.466 --> 00:00:59.199
They're attached back to back right now,

00:00:59.199 --> 00:01:01.732
and they've got a nice clean design.

00:01:05.732 --> 00:01:06.966
Now, if we take a look at the

00:01:06.966 --> 00:01:11.399
portal app,
we can adjust the different parameters

00:01:11.399 --> 00:01:14.399
and see relevant info,
which is very handy.

00:01:15.799 --> 00:01:17.899
Got the portals on the table right now,

00:01:17.899 --> 00:01:21.299
but we're going to put them on the floor
to have more working area.

00:01:30.866 --> 00:01:33.866
So we can increase the width...

00:01:35.532 --> 00:01:38.532
width. The height

00:01:39.532 --> 00:01:42.532
and turn on the lights on the sides.

00:01:44.199 --> 00:01:47.166
And can change the color.

00:01:47.166 --> 00:01:49.799
It's currently red,
but you can't really see

00:01:49.799 --> 00:01:52.799
in this lighting.

00:01:56.366 --> 00:01:59.366
Well, let's get them on the walls.

00:01:59.832 --> 00:02:03.199
We can have one on the left
panel of that door,

00:02:03.432 --> 00:02:06.432
and one next to the outlet over there.

00:02:07.832 --> 00:02:09.366
One thing to note is the once

00:02:09.366 --> 00:02:12.566
you separate the two portals,
you can't change the size anymore.

00:02:12.899 --> 00:02:16.399
And both portals have some gecko material
on the back to grab onto

00:02:16.399 --> 00:02:17.566
most flat surfaces.

00:02:20.366 --> 00:02:23.099
Okay, now the portals are installed.

00:02:23.099 --> 00:02:26.099
We can now press the activate button.

00:02:30.166 --> 00:02:32.999
Whoa.

00:02:32.999 --> 00:02:35.766
That's trippy.

00:02:35.766 --> 00:02:39.632
Well, seems like everything's
working properly.

00:02:39.699 --> 00:02:42.232
Now let's get a closer look.

00:02:42.232 --> 00:02:45.199
So if I wave my left hand into this portal,

00:02:45.199 --> 00:02:48.199
we’re supposed to see it on the left.

00:02:49.032 --> 00:02:52.199
And if I wave my right hand into the left portal,

00:02:52.199 --> 00:02:54.266
we're supposed to see on the right.

00:02:55.399 --> 00:02:58.399
Yeah.

00:02:58.832 --> 00:02:59.466
Overall,

00:02:59.466 --> 00:03:03.166
I think it's really cool to have something
so lightweight and convenient.

00:03:03.632 --> 00:03:04.799
I haven't done much research

00:03:04.799 --> 00:03:08.132
into the security features,
but I do trust Safe-Portals on this.

00:03:08.666 --> 00:03:10.832
I definitely recommend this product.

00:03:10.832 --> 00:03:13.732
You can purchase it on the Safe-Portals
official website,

00:03:13.732 --> 00:03:17.132
or click the link in the description below
for a 20% discount.

00:03:17.332 --> 00:03:20.066
Don't forget to like and subscribe
for more videos.

00:03:20.066 --> 00:03:21.266
See you next time!

